      "line_range": "9",
      "translation": "(ii 1') ........ He made the dragon raise its neck high . ... manu - wood .... Its ... did sit in the ... for him . You did capture the dragon and kill it ; you indeed made it lie at your feet ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001534.17",
      "line_range": "17",
      "translation": "(iii 1') My father , although it was a warrior , I did kill the Six-headed wild ram in its mountain ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001534.20",
      "line_range": "20",
      "translation": "(iii 4') The Date palm grew very tall over the mountain , the pure place ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001534.22",
      "line_range": "22",
      "translation": "(iv 1') Because ....., ... do not eat good food ; do not drink fresh water in Ŋirsu ."
    }
  ],
